03\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">103</biblScope></bibl>, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0027.tlg001.perseus-grc1:126\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ And.\">And.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">1.126</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κατάρχομαι μέν, σφάγια δ᾽ ἄλλοισιν μέλει</foreign> I <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">begin the rite</tr_>, but leave the slaughter of the victim to others, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0006.tlg013.perseus-grc1:40\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ E.\">E.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ IT\">IT</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">40</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπὶ τῶν θυσιῶν κριθαῖς κ</foreign>. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0081.tlg001:2:25\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ D.H.\">D.H.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">2.25</biblScope> </bibl>: c. gen., <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">κατάρχεσθαι τοῦ τράγου</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">make a beginning of</tr_> the victim, i. e. <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">consecrate</tr_> him <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">for sacrifice</tr_> by cutting off the hair of his forehead, <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg006.perseus-grc1:959\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Av.\">Av.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">959</biblScope> </bibl>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">ἐπεὶ δὲ αὐτοῦ</foreign> (sc. <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">Ἡρακλέος</foreign>)<cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">πρὸς τῷ βωμῷ κατάρχοντο</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg